《'''心灵鸡汤'''》（{{lang-en|''Chicken Soup for the Soul''}}）是由一系列[[书籍|书籍]]组成的一个书籍组的名称，通常有具有灵感和激励性的短篇故事和散文组成，该书的作者是{{link-en|杰克·坎菲尔|Jack Canfield}}与{{link-en|马克·汉森|Mark Victor Hansen}}。

《心灵鸡汤》超过200种类别，有许多书籍都是针对特定的人群，如：母亲鸡汤、囚犯鸡汤、祖父鸡汤、祖母鸡汤、孩子鸡汤、父亲鸡汤。

== 历史 ==
第一系列《心灵鸡汤》印制和出版了数百万份。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicken Soup for the Soul|url=https://www.chickensoup.com/books?cid=titles|accessdate=2020-07-13|work=www.chickensoup.com|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316015512/https://www.chickensoup.com/books?cid=titles|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前，全世界54种语言一亿份书籍正在印制和出版。《心灵鸡汤》少女系列超过14种，专门卖给[[美国|美国]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[英国|英国]]和[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]的少女。

《心灵鸡汤》还包括一系列的小制品小作品，包括[[贺卡|贺卡]]、[[挂历|挂历]]、[[礼包|礼包]]、[[宠物食品|宠物食品]]、[[服装|服装]]、[[游戏碟|游戏碟]]、[[DVD|DVD]]、《[[圣经|圣经]]》。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Home {{!}} Chicken Soup for the Soul Pet Food|url=https://chickensouppets.com/|accessdate=2020-07-13|work=chickensouppets.com|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316013502/https://chickensouppets.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.a-egroup.com/ae/photogallery/thumbnails.php?album=13 Chicken Soup for the Soul sleepwear] {{Wayback|url=http://www.a-egroup.com/ae/photogallery/thumbnails.php?album=13 |date=20120307204643 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kappapublishing.com/kappabooks/pages/puzzles.html |title=Chicken Soup for the Soul puzzle books |access-date=2012-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223192559/http://www.kappapublishing.com/kappabooks/pages/puzzles.html |archive-date=2012-02-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.countyourblessingsgame.com/ |title=Chicken Soup for the Soul Count Your Blessings board game |access-date=2012-03-02 |archive-date=2021-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316013445/http://www.countyourblessingsgame.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1999年，[[杰西卡·萨弗拉|杰西卡·萨弗拉]]出版了《爱情心灵鸡汤》。

书籍命名为《心灵鸡汤》是为了治疗[[家庭|家庭]]病人，培养他们健康的身体和良好的品质。<ref name="about">{{Cite web|title=About Chicken Soup for the Soul {{!}} Chicken Soup for the Soul|url=https://www.chickensoup.com/about/what-is-chicken-soup-for-the-soul|accessdate=2020-07-13|date=2014-02-06|work=www.chickensoup.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316013442/https://www.chickensoup.com/about/what-is-chicken-soup-for-the-soul|dead-url=no}}</ref>

从1993年到2008年，《心灵鸡汤》由创始人[[杰克·坎菲尔|杰克·坎菲尔]]与[[马克·汉森|马克·汉森]]负责出版和发行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/print/20090202/11989-serving-up-a-new-chicken-soup-.html |title=Serving Up A New Chicken Soup |accessdate=2012-03-02 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918031807/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/print/20090202/11989-serving-up-a-new-chicken-soup-.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《心灵鸡汤》开设了一个娱乐区，可供人们观看家庭电影和视频点播。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.homemediamagazine.com/tv-dvd/screen-media-distribute-chicken-soup-soul-18082|title=Screen Media to Distribute Chicken Soup for the Soul|accessdate=12 January 2010|author=Lopez, Justine|work=Home Media Magazine|publisher=|language=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229173832/http://www.homemediamagazine.com/tv-dvd/screen-media-distribute-chicken-soup-soul-18082|archivedate=2012年2月29日|df=}}</ref>

而受《心灵鸡汤》影响，一些励志性或者启发性文章也被成为“鸡汤文”<ref>{{Cite web|title=为什么有的人爱看心灵鸡汤文？|url=http://help.3g.163.com/15/0702/11/ATH2KMG000964LD0.html|accessdate=2020-07-13|date=2015-07-02|last=网易|work=help.3g.163.com|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124035127/http://help.3g.163.com/15/0702/11/ATH2KMG000964LD0.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

